<function>

access:   public

name: fetchAll

param: string|array, $tags, NULL

param: string|array, $where, NULL

param: string|array, $order, NULL

param: int, $page, NULL

return: array

</function>

Fetch a list of nodes of the master node type.

* Parameters:

 * string|array //$tags//: Fetch nodes with all these tags; if empty, ignores tags.

 * string|array //$where//: A set of multiWhere() conditions to determine which nodes are fetched.

 * string|array //$order//: Order the returned rows in this fashion.

 * int //$page//: Which page-number of results to fetch.

* Returns array: The list of nodes.

Fetch a list of nodes of the master node type.